##
##  `intersection'&Elements that form a modulo pcgs for the intersection of
##  both subgroups.
##
##  `factorization'&A function that returns for an element <x> in the span
##  of `sum' a record with components `u' and `n' that give its
##  decomposition.
##  \enditems
